[[美國|美國]][[電視連續劇|電視連續劇]]'''[[迷失|迷失]]'''的'''第三季'''於2006年10月4日在美國及[[加拿大|加拿大]]地區首播，並於2007年5月23日結束。第一集開始的68天之前超過40人的一隊生還者乘飛機墜落在南太平洋一處荒島，而本季繼續描述他們在島上的生存故事。<ref>Fordis, Jeff, (January 22, 2007) "[http://www.abcmedianet.com/assets/pr/html/012207_15.html The Life of One of "The Others" Rests in Jack's Hands, on the Return of ABC's ''Lost''] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927201428/http://www.abcmedianet.com/assets/pr/html/012207_15.html |date=2007-09-27 }}," 'ABC Medianet.  Retrieved on September 7, 2007.</ref>在迷失劇情裏面，第三季從2004年11月28日開始直到2004年12月23日。製片者說，第一季描述生還者的性格，第二季描述島上的艙口，而第三季便會描述“其他人”——荒島上面一群神秘的原著人。<ref>Aurthur, Kate, (May 25, 2006) "[http://www.nytimes.com/2006/05/25/arts/television/25lost.html?ei=5088&en=2d1372ad803eb440&ex=1306209600&pagewanted=print Dickens, Challah and That Mysterious Island] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2006/05/25/arts/television/25lost.html?ei=5088&en=2d1372ad803eb440&ex=1306209600&pagewanted=print |date=20090126192330 }}," ''The New York Times''.  Retrieved on September 9, 2007.</ref>

爲了響應粉絲們對前一季節目安排的不滿，第三季分兩段播放並且不會重播。<ref>Covel, Bonnie, (October 3, 2006) "[http://lost.about.com/od/creationoflost/a/Jjabramslost.htm J·J·亞伯拉罕 Talks About ''Lost'' and His Other Shows] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071219091412/http://lost.about.com/od/creationoflost/a/Jjabramslost.htm |date=2007-12-19 }}," ''[[About.com|About.com]]''.  Retrieved on September 7, 2007.</ref>在美國，第一段包含6集節目，並且於每個星期三晚上9點鐘播映，12星期的停頓後，將會在晚上10點鐘播放餘下的16集。<ref>Mahan, Colin, (July 18, 2006) "[http://www.tv.com/story/5400.html?q=lost%20broken&tag=search_results;title;0 ''Lost'' will be Broken in Two] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tv.com/story/5400.html?q=lost%20broken&tag=search_results;title;0 |date=20070929150826 }}," ''TV.com''.  Retrieved on September 8, 2007.</ref>除此之外，另加三集節目重溫過去兩季所發生的事件。“Lost: A Tale of Survival”在第一集首播前1星期播映，“Lost Survivor Guide”於第二段之前播出，<ref>Fordis, Jeff, (January 22, 2007) "[http://www.abcmedianet.com/web/progcal/dispDNR.aspx?id=012207_14 Lost Survivor Guide] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930165323/http://www.abcmedianet.com/web/progcal/dispDNR.aspx?id=012207_14 |date=2007-09-30 }}," ABC Medianet.  Retrieved on September 7, 2007.</ref>而“Lost: The Answers”在最後一集前播放。<ref>Fordis, Jeff, (April 30, 2007) "[http://www.abcmedianet.com/web/progcal/dispDNR.aspx?id=043007_13 Lost: The Answers] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930155344/http://www.abcmedianet.com/web/progcal/dispDNR.aspx?id=043007_13 |date=2007-09-30 }}," ''ABC Studios''.  Retrieved on September 7, 2007.</ref>Buena Vista Home Entertainment於2007年12月11日在[[數位影碟區域碼|區域1]]發佈的DVD標題為Lost: The Complete Third Season – The Unexplored Experience，<ref>Buena Vista Home Entertainment, (2007) "[http://abctvstore.seenon.com/detail.php?p=24760&v=lost ''Lost - The Complete Third Season''] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080603054840/http://abctvstore.seenon.com/detail.php?p=24760&v=lost |date=2008-06-03 }}," ''American Broadcasting Company''.  Retrieved on September 9, 2007.</ref>DVD可為7碟盒裝或者6碟[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]盒裝。<ref>Snugglefish Media, (August 31, 2007) "[http://bluray.highdefdigest.com/news/show/Disney/TV_on_High-Def/Disney_Reveals_New_Specs,_Exclusive_Extras_for_Lost:_Third_Season_Blu-ray_/917 Disney Reveals New Specs, Exclusive Extras for ''Lost: Third Season'' Blu-ray] {{Wayback|url=http://bluray.highdefdigest.com/news/show/Disney/TV_on_High-Def/Disney_Reveals_New_Specs,_Exclusive_Extras_for_Lost:_Third_Season_Blu-ray_/917 |date=20071111181814 }}," ''High-Def Digest''.  Retrieved on September 9 2007.</ref>

== 人員 ==
本季由Touchstone Television（現為ABC Studios）、Bad Robot Productions和Grass Skirt Productions製作並由[[美國廣播公司|美國廣播公司]]於[[美國|美國]]放映。第三季的執行製作者為[[J·J·亞伯拉罕|J·J·亞伯拉罕]]、[[戴蒙·林道夫|戴蒙·林道夫]]、[[布萊恩·布爾克|布萊恩·布爾克]]、[[傑克·本德|傑克·本德]]、[[傑夫·平克納|傑夫·平克納]]和[[卡爾頓·丘斯|卡爾頓·丘斯]]。<ref>[[戴蒙·林道夫|Lindelof, Damon]], (January 2007) "[http://www.abcmedianet.com/web/showpage/showpage.aspx?program_id=001648&type=producers ''Lost'' Producers] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930171025/http://www.abcmedianet.com/web/showpage/showpage.aspx?program_id=001648&type=producers |date=2007-09-30 }}," ABC Medianet.  Retrieved on September 7, 2007.</ref>  The staff writers were Lindelof, Cuse, Pinkner, co-executive producers [[愛德華·克特西斯|愛德華·克特西斯]]和[[亞當·霍若維玆|亞當·霍若維玆]], co-executive producer [[Drew_Goddard|Drew Goddard]], supervising producer [[伊利沙伯·薩諾夫|伊利沙伯·薩諾夫]], story editor [[克利斯丁娜·M·金|克利斯丁娜·M·金]] and executive story editor [[Brian_K._Vaughan|Brian K. Vaughan]].<ref>Goldman, Eric, (December 26, 2006) "[http://tv.ign.com/articles/752/752170p1.html Comic Book Writer Gets ''Lost''] {{Wayback|url=http://tv.ign.com/articles/752/752170p1.html |date=20070219124014 }}," ''[[IGN|IGN]]''.  Retrieved on September 1, 2007.</ref>而常規的導演為本德、監督製作者[[史提芬·威廉斯|史提芬·威廉斯]]、[[保羅·愛德華玆|保羅·愛德華玆]]和[[Eric_Laneuville|Eric Laneuville]]，林道夫和丘斯為節目管理者。<ref>Keller, Joel, (January 15, 2007) "[http://www.tvsquad.com/2007/01/15/abcs-show-runners-talk-about-pitching-network-notes-and-inter ABC's Show Runners Talk About Pitching, Network Notes, and Internet Scrutiny] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tvsquad.com/2007/01/15/abcs-show-runners-talk-about-pitching-network-notes-and-inter |date=20090218191212 }}," ''TV Squad''.  Retrieved on August 30, 2007.</ref>

